title: Gradient Explainer; LookupError: gradient registry has no entry for: shap_StridedSlice

labels.name: bug
labels.description: Indicates an unexpected problem or unintended behaviour

labels.name: awaiting feedback
labels.description: Indicates that further information is required from the issue creator

body:
I am running the following code:

```
import shap 

explainer = shap.GradientExplainer(model, x_train)
shap_values = explainer.shap_values(x_test[:10])
```

I run into the following error:
```
LookupError: gradient registry has no entry for: shap_StridedSlice
```
Here is a summary of my model:
```
Model: "sequential_6"
_________________________________________________________________
Layer (type)                 Output Shape              Param #   
=================================================================
simple_rnn_6 (SimpleRNN)     (None, 10, 1)             12        
_________________________________________________________________
dense_6 (Dense)              (None, 10, 1)             2         
_________________________________________________________________
flatten (Flatten)            (None, 10)                0         
=================================================================
Total params: 14
Trainable params: 14
Non-trainable params: 0
_________________________________________________________________
```
My SHAP and TensorFlow versions are

* **shap**: 0.35.0
* **tensorflow**: 2.3.0
